{"tid":573242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你老母個臭化系","createTime":"2018-02-26T09:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T09:57:43.000Z","uid":153790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f30a24991d80254cfaaf91c70e6eae1643ee12","tid":573242,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"一齊幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 忍撚左你好耐<br />\n今日終於忍唔住爆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一半經常唔覆whatsapp<br />\n一覆就係4-8個鐘後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說今日佢無番工<br />\n都可以唔撚覆我<br />\n我要求已經好撚低<br />\n我同佢講：你番工唔覆、唔打電話、唔搵我都可以！我接受你番工攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 今日問佢做咩唔覆whatsapp<br />\n佢答：一時唔記得覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌！我即刻扯火<br />\n不如下次你答唔記得有另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 點解可以成日唔覆機<br />\n點解可以咁撚賤格<br />\n明明要求都咁撚低<br />\n只求一覆 但唔係半日後覆姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌屌屌屌屌！爆出黎"},{"pid":"c246a93d80d4db6f03c390b3eb7675f35af6e215","tid":573242,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"講佢2句！whatsapp封撚埋我！<br />\n屌！又係我錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚嬲"},{"pid":"ec9a113fc4b44e82aeed9c6e37d364e65d3f952b","tid":573242,"uid":85592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"咁佢點？"},{"pid":"c3bf469c8d556f8d60f72e2c797058b86f8b0fd6","tid":573242,"uid":95470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"點睇都係佢識左第二個<br />\nor 已經對你冇feel 分手啦"},{"pid":"7f3570e54d8d609c450bd4ee4c4b37a61472d0ee","tid":573242,"uid":90476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"條女比綠帽你帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor